                "content": "I know myself: I still think about our wedding budget crisis \u2014 how we stretched every rupee but refused to cut corners on the things that actually mattered.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970575Z"
              },
              {
                "id": "24a6b5d0-295a-45a2-942d-9ccf52b496f2",
                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970642Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "What matters most to me: Quality over price",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970642Z"
              },
              {
                "id": "a7c67d14-6688-433a-8314-c51e55bbe47c",
                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970708Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "Something I always navigate: You tend to be high price-sensitive \u2014 you consistently seek deals and carefully weigh every purchase against your available budget before committing.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970708Z"
              },
              {
                "id": "0f00ee27-903c-4c08-830c-e96af0ccbdfe",
                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970736Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "A defining moment in my life: While planning her wedding in Kochi, she insisted on a quality catering spread despite her family's tight budget, and watched relatives quietly judge the modest venue while praising the food \u2014 a painful lesson in choosing battles. \u2014 Cemented her belief that quality in the right places matters more than quantity everywhere, fueling her ongoing tension between spending wisely and refusing to compromise on what truly matters.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970736Z"
              },
              {
                "id": "dddeb402-ef50-4144-9347-aaa6fb16a287",
                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970764Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "A defining moment in my life: When her infant daughter spiked a high fever at 2 AM, she called her mother in Thrissur before the doctor, and her mother's calm guidance got them through the night without an emergency visit. \u2014 Deepened her trust in family over institutions, and reinforced her low risk tolerance \u2014 she now over-prepares for every household decision, especially anything involving her child's health or safety.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970764Z"
              },
              {
                "id": "03a86ce5-741a-4d77-9968-c36a40939402",
                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970789Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "A defining moment in my life: She brought an elaborate home-cooked Kerala fish curry to an office potluck only to have a colleague loudly avoid it claiming gluten concerns, which confused her since the dish had none \u2014 the moment felt dismissive of her effort. \u2014 Left her skeptical of trendy dietary labels like gluten-free or keto, viewing them as largely performative for people around her, and reinforced her preference for traditional, wholesome home cooking.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T02:35:06.970789Z"
              }
            ],
