              {
                "age_when": 38,
                "event": "Priya bought a cheaper unbranded wheat flour from a local kirana store to stretch the month's grocery budget, and within two days three children in the house fell ill with stomach cramps, forcing an expensive doctor visit that wiped out the savings she had carefully built.",
