                "lasting_impact": "He stopped seeking external validation for his intellectual judgments and developed a deep self-trust orientation, while his commitment to rigorous, quality-first thinking only intensified."
              },
              {
                "age_when": 25,
                "event": "Three months into his first full-time tech role in Bengaluru, he methodically automated his entire personal finance workflow \u2014 SIPs, bill payments, and discretionary tracking \u2014 through a combination of UPI-linked apps and custom scripts, eliminating every cash or manual transaction from his life.",
